        <td>≥97–98%</td>
        <td class="ref"><a href="https://www.unleashedsoftware.com/blog/inventory-cycle-count/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Unleashed</a> · <a href="https://www.cadretech.com/blog/warehouse-kpis/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CadreTech</a></td>
