      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Encogimiento típico (stretch)</td>
        <td>10–18%</td>
        <td class="ref"><a href="https://www.onlineclothingstudy.com/2015/04/control-fabric-shrinkage-in-garment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Online Clothing Study</a></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Tolerancia largo rollos (punto)</td>
        <td>±2,0%</td>
        <td class="ref"><a href="https://www.ethiostandards.org/sites/default/files/2021-01/13%20Specification%20for%20tolerances%20of%20Knitted%20Fabrics.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ES 6731:2021</a></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Tolerancias equipo de medición</td>
        <td>p.ej. 10–11 yd: ¾″ sub / ⅜″ sobre</td>
